{"tid":487082,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"藍田匯景東方食神","createTime":"2017-12-02T12:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T12:30:07.000Z","uid":6267,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5f9bee6a1c48ecb16364c150864a8a27946db5a4","tid":487082,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:16:39.000Z","msg":"叫左三個人唔該想叫野，<br />\n<br />\n都係講句得，有個伙記向我張枱行過黎，<br />\n<br />\n叫兩三句唔該先望過黎，話做乜撚野！<br />\n<br />\n態度差到唔會再去！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/201620_532fbd6fadf05f804bb51088aa4a5a17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F201620_532fbd6fadf05f804bb51088aa4a5a17.jpg&h=7e5d4cd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1e936e912f915ee62b5743478057dd7aa9f8882","tid":487082,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾黎"},{"pid":"cfd3a4142d037d6035a71c75b0dbdbd48f2ff5a2","tid":487082,"uid":86837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 估唔到間野未執"},{"pid":"dfa4d793f907e34845b332d80ea3671dff9c4154","tid":487082,"uid":86837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:18:38.000Z","msg":"野食又唔係特別好味都咁鬼串咁鬼惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10790169097b11f29b5075b6d15c5e80ea7a9442","tid":487082,"uid":128231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:20:10.000Z","msg":"中學回憶"},{"pid":"cb1bee883a760104e7854ae051015959fedf495e","tid":487082,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:22:32.000Z","msg":"其實好唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fddd333aaa53cc8a9b7b67d5f27a8c459dd444d","tid":487082,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實好唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通，但佢近，先會去食咁多次！<br />\n<br />\n經過呢次我唔會再食，俾錢買難受，<br />\n<br />\n佢地真係有病，叫極唔應都夠離譜，<br />\n<br />\n仲要用粗口，叫埋朋友罷去"},{"pid":"0368dc8894336d12d8836611f274e496dcd5e37e","tid":487082,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:40:05.000Z","msg":"車仔面？"},{"pid":"9521e6c49bea5a800fd7e4d6f4af68c0916367fd","tid":487082,"uid":54472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:42:31.000Z","msg":"間野真係唔多掂 野食又唔係好 啲位又窄又唔好坐"},{"pid":"38ff863be929479133f926ac21c5285e7e4935c0","tid":487082,"uid":1330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:53:59.000Z","msg":"樓主走咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3030fe059130fdc117dca70f84d6dbe70fdf21","tid":487082,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主走咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n晏就既事"},{"pid":"060170efe7ba1e96dbd6188465a4ce2092237dff","tid":487082,"uid":140411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T13:36:13.000Z","msg":"真係叫做普通三十幾蚊嘅車仔麵   味道都係好普通 <br />\n但係啲伙記嘅態度唔好就真係扣曬分<br />\n試過一次之後 我都知道冇下次"},{"pid":"a40e26da3acfe8c67620e5d8265fee65e238a106","tid":487082,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"30蚊唔包服務費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  果間野出名差 但省錢又唔洗餓都算係咁"},{"pid":"540a34e56ce8ac042510978653f516aedb5e5ff2","tid":487082,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>30蚊唔包服務費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  果間野出名差 但省錢又唔洗餓都算係咁</blockquote><br />\n咁我俾多10幾去食榮嫂啦！<br />\n<br />\n唔係要酒店服務，但唔係用粗口囉！<br />\n<br />\n牛奶公司咩"},{"pid":"22ed2b1254dcad78287838faaa51c0327da408c8","tid":487082,"uid":7306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"做乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港服務業真係世界級"},{"pid":"0a5a4c5453d11868ae816bcc1c32f1051fbed30e","tid":487082,"uid":67448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T23:30:32.000Z","msg":"以前觀塘有檔野同佢一樣名，10蚊好撚大兜炒米，1蚊件煎釀三寶，之後執左，唔係係咪呢檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611570bc82ad3717db5b0d82155c02f005082b53","tid":487082,"uid":124414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:04:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港服務業真係世界級</blockquote><br />\n這就是香港"},{"pid":"1a983fc7bfd3943b80efa75bdac06cc83d21ac77","tid":487082,"uid":6778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:06:56.000Z","msg":"未落單咪出門口走  問你做乜撚野 你仲繼續落單照食 真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"99484e145d08141578c9ae6ef9f2a499b1a03d98","tid":487082,"uid":113853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:14:42.000Z","msg":"好難食"},{"pid":"d8be6e680aaaff4d4aeff5a5f9a202ef1fb38989","tid":487082,"uid":107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"呢間車仔麵係垃圾，只可以食炸脾炒一丁，個個月都最少食一次。"},{"pid":"4e4a209652920784f5a52ac25540ac80c73fbe71","tid":487082,"uid":50550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:30:07.000Z","msg":"最後你咪又係照叫野食, 佢唔怕你唔返黎食"}]}